Record Class ControllerState

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
fr.connexe.ui.game.input.ControllerState
Record Components:
slot - the index of the controller in the controllers array
dpadLeftPressed - true when the left D-pad button is pressed
dpadRightPressed - true when the right D-pad button is pressed
dpadUpPressed - true when the up D-pad button is pressed
dpadDownPressed - true when the down D-pad button is pressed
leftJoystickX - position of the left joystick X-axis, ranging from -1.0 to 1.0
leftJoystickY - position of the left joystick Y-axis, ranging from -1.0 to 1.0
rightJoystickX - position of the right joystick X-axis, ranging from -1.0 to 1.0
rightJoystickY - position of the right joystick Y-axis, ranging from -1.0 to 1.0
public record ControllerState(int slot, boolean dpadLeftPressed, boolean dpadRightPressed, boolean dpadUpPressed, boolean dpadDownPressed, float leftJoystickX, float leftJoystickY, float rightJoystickX, float rightJoystickY) extends Record
The state of a controller's buttons and joysticks.
